      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. BEFORE THE DAWN is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.77 beating Linkin Park. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Well placed and will be tough to beat. 8. CAWBOURNE ZARA has a strong winning strike-rate over this journey with two wins and a placing from four tries. Comes off a (24.91) win last time, scoring by half a length in a Grade 5 over 440m at Goulburn. Can feature with the right run. 2. TAKE A BREAK has been hard to follow lately, running sixth (30.20) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Wentworth Park. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. 3. ZIPPING CRUELLA will make her presence felt following a brief layoff.\",\"runners\":[1,8,2,3],\"exclusive\":false}",
